---

Note: This project drives OwnTone (https://github.com/owntone/owntone-server,
GPLv2) as a separate, unmodified-at-runtime AirPlay 2 sender via its HTTP API
and a named pipe. OwnTone is not bundled in this repository; setup.sh builds it
from source. AirPlay 2 support in OwnTone derives from community reverse
engineering and may break with Apple/HomePod updates.
